OL,3,C'Disgusted' Wolves stands with striker
OL,4,CTolu Arokodare after racial abuse
OL,6,FWolverhampton Wanderers have said it's
OL,7,F'disgusted' after striker Tolu
OL,8,FArokodare was racially abused online.
OL,10,FIt came after the club's 1-0 loss away
OL,11,Fto Crystal Palace on Sunday (February
OL,12,F22nd).
OL,14,FIn the game, the 25-year-old had the
OL,15,Fchance to put Wolves ahead with a
OL,16,Fpenalty, but his effort was saved by
OL,17,FDean Henderson.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771882264
OL,3,C'Disgusted' Wolves stands with striker
OL,4,CTolu Arokodare after racial abuse
OL,6,FA few hours after the game, the club
OL,7,Freleased a statement in which they
OL,8,Fsaid they 'condemn this abhorrent and
OL,9,Funlawful behaviour in the strongest
OL,10,Fpossible terms'.
OL,12,FThey added that 'Tolu has our full and
OL,13,Funwavering support'.
OL,15,FArokodare shared the private messages
OL,16,Fon his Instagram page and followed it
OL,17,Fwith a statement in which he said
OL,18,Fthose responsible should be punished.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771882264
OL,3,C'Disgusted' Wolves stands with striker
OL,4,CTolu Arokodare after racial abuse
OL,6,FHe said: "It's still unbelievable to
OL,7,Fme that we're playing in a time where
OL,8,Fpeople have so much freedom to
OL,9,Fcommunicate such racism wihtout any
OL,10,Fconsequences.
OL,12,F"These individuals should have no
OL,13,Fplace in our game, and collectively we
OL,14,Fhave to take action to punish everyone
OL,15,Fwho taints the sport like this, no
OL,16,Fmatter who they are."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771882264
OL,3,C'Disgusted' Wolves stands with striker
OL,4,CTolu Arokodare after racial abuse
OL,6,FIn a statement, the club said: "Wolves
OL,7,Fare disgusted by numerous instances of
OL,8,Fracist abuse, from multiple
OL,9,Fperpetrators, directed at Tolu
OL,10,FArokodare on social media following
OL,11,Ftoday's fixture against Crystal Palace.
OL,13,F"There is no place for racism ` in
OL,14,Ffootball, online, or anywhere in
OL,15,Fsociety.
OL,17,F"We condemn this abhorrent and
OL,18,Funlawful behaviour in the strongest
OL,19,Fpossible terms. Tolu has our full and
OL,20,Funwavering support.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771882264
OL,3,C'Disgusted' Wolves stands with striker
OL,4,CTolu Arokodare after racial abuse
OL,6,F"No player should be subjected to such
OL,7,Fhatred simply for doing their job. We
OL,8,Fstand firmly alongside him, and
OL,9,Falongside all footballers who are
OL,10,Fforced to endure this abuse from
OL,11,Fanonymous accounts acting with
OL,12,Fapparent impunity.
OL,14,F"The club has reported the posts to
OL,15,Fthe relevant platforms and will work
OL,16,Fwith the Premier League and the
OL,17,Fauthorities to help identify those
OL,18,Fresponsible and ensure appropriate
OL,19,Faction is taken.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1771882264
OL,3,C'Disgusted' Wolves stands with striker
OL,4,CTolu Arokodare after racial abuse
OL,6,F"We will continue to take a zero-
OL,7,Ftolerance approach to all forms of
OL,8,Fdiscrimination."
OL,10,FAs well as posting the statement on
OL,11,Fsocial media, Wolves also included
OL,12,Fscreenshots of some of the messages
OL,13,Fthat were sent to Arokodare.
OL,15,FArokodare was the fourth player to be
OL,16,Fsent racial abuse this weekend.
OL,17,FChelsea's Wesley Fofana, Sunderland's
OL,18,FRomaine Mundle and Burnley's Hannibal
OL,19,FMejbri also received messages.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
